@macncheesepaint @PatrickoftheG @LakotaMan1 It is a graphic novel, a graphic adaptation of the original diary and based on Anne's words, it opens up the diary to a new audience, in the same way that the video diary produced by the Anne Frank House does.
@shaeburks @LakotaMan1 The illustrated version is based on Anne's words, there is nothing there that wasn't in the original version of the diary
